Build instructions

Install libfreenect.

Then type:
	scons
	sudo scons install

OS X build instructions

libfreenect required to be an universal build.
	Make a directory 'build' in the repo directory
	Go into that directory
	Type ccmake ..
	press 'c' for configure, then change CMAKE_OSX_ARCHITECTURES to "i386 -arch x86_64"
	configure and generate, then type make
	sudo make install

